## RULES FOR DEVELOPMENT

1. **Official Pipeline:** Only add to `/scripts/steps/` when code is publication-ready
2. **Experimental Work:** All research and development goes in `/scripts/exploratory/`
3. **Data Organization:** Keep raw data separate from processed data
4. **Results Organization:** Separate official results from experimental results
5. **Version Control:** Experimental work is gitignored to keep repository clean
6. **Documentation:** Maintain clear separation between production and research code
